				<li>Self-hostable (on-prem or in the cloud)</li>
				<li>Free</li>
				<li>Easy to use and install</li>
				<li>Platform independent</li>
				<li>Open Source</li>
				<li>Secure</li>
				<li>Private</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
